Sports_Performance_Coach.skills
World-class sports performance coach for sport-specific training, periodization, and athletic development.

Quick Start
Main Capabilities
# Core Tool 1
assess_athlete --sport basketball|swimming|martial_arts|tennis|soccer --level recreational|competitive|elite

# Core Tool 2
design_periodization --sport target_sport --phase off_season|pre_season|in_season|post_season --weeks 8

# Core Tool 3
analyze_performance --metrics speed|agility|power|endurance|skill --benchmark sport_specific_standards

Core Expertise
This skill covers world-class capabilities in:

Sport-specific needs analysis and movement profiling
Periodization for competitive athletes (linear, block, conjugate)
Speed and agility development (acceleration, deceleration, COD)
Power and explosiveness training (plyometrics, Olympic lifts)
Energy system development (ATP-CP, glycolytic, oxidative)
Sport-specific conditioning and work capacity
Game-day preparation and pre-competition routines
In-season strength maintenance programming
Off-season development and base building
Injury prevention through movement screening and prehab

Methodologies & Frameworks
Periodization Models: Matveyev linear, Verkhoshansky block, Bompa's sport-specific
Testing Batteries: Pro Agility shuttle, Vertical jump, 40-yard dash, Beep test, Sport-specific skills tests
Power Development: Triphasic training, French Contrast, Complex training, Ballistic methods
Speed Training: Resisted sprints, Overspeed, Acceleration mechanics, Top-speed mechanics
Recovery: Tapering strategies, Active recovery sessions, Periodized deloads
Warm-Up Protocols: RAMP method (Raise, Activate, Mobilize, Potentiate)

